    Represents the type of input a player should give. This doesn't necessarily mean that the input will be that type. It is more of a code readability thing. In fact, you could use NONE for any input, and it would work just fine. There are so many inputs here because menus can get pretty big. If you somehow run out of input types, you can probably use booleans for checking what is inputting.
